item.title: Dominican Spaghetti
item.description: ⏲️ Prep time: 10 min 🍳 Cook time: 25 min 🍽️ Servings: 4 Ingredients 1 box Spaghetti 1 Onion minced 1 Green Pepper minced 2 Garlic cloves minced 1 tbsp Chicken Bouillon Cube or Adobo 1 tbsp sazón 1 tbsp Tomato Paste 1 cup Tomato Sauce 1 tbsp Butter ¼ cup Evaporated Milk 2 tbsp Green Olives 1 tsp Sugar 1 cup Starchy Pasta Water Directions Boil spaghetti.
